              <li>AI visibility audit &amp; baseline</li>
              <li>Schema markup implementation</li>
              <li>Content optimisation (5 pages/mo)</li>
              <li>llms.txt setup &amp; maintenance</li>
              <li>Monthly AI visibility report</li>
              <li>Quarterly strategy review</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-secondary">Get Started</a>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-card featured reveal reveal-d2">
            <h3>Growth</h3>
            <div class="price">$5,000 <span>SGD/mo</span></div>
            <p class="pricing-desc">For businesses ready to dominate AI recommendations.</p>
            <ul class="pricing-features">
              <li>Everything in Essentials</li>
              <li>Content optimisation (20 pages/mo)</li>
              <li>Authority building &amp; directory registrations</li>
              <li>Answer Engine content creation</li>
              <li>Bi-weekly reporting with competitor benchmarks</li>
              <li>Dedicated GEO strategist</li>
              <li>Content freshness programme</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-card reveal reveal-d3">
            <h3>Enterprise</h3>
            <div class="price">$10,000+ <span>SGD/mo</span></div>
            <p class="pricing-desc">Full-service AI search domination across all platforms.</p>
            <ul class="pricing-features">
              <li>Everything in Growth</li>
              <li>Multi-platform defensive monitoring</li>
              <li>Wikipedia presence strategy</li>
              <li>Weekly strategy calls &amp; real-time dashboard</li>
              <li>Custom prompt monitoring (50+ prompts daily)</li>
              <li>Sentiment defence &amp; crisis alerts</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-secondary">Let's Talk</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="section-content reveal" style="margin-top: 2rem; text-align: center;">
        <p>Full service details on our <a href="/services/ai-search-optimisation/" class="inline-link">AI Search Optimisation</a> page.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== FAQ ========== -->
  <section class="section faq-section" id="faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions about getting recommended by ChatGPT">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <p class="section-label">FAQ</p>
        <h2>ChatGPT Recommendation Questions Answered</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d1">
          <summary>Why doesn't ChatGPT recommend my business?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>ChatGPT doesn't use Google rankings to decide which brands to recommend. It relies on entity clarity, structured data, content quality, and third-party mentions across the web. If your brand lacks these signals, ChatGPT simply won't know enough about you to recommend you confidently.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d2">
          <summary>How does ChatGPT decide which brands to recommend?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>ChatGPT selects brands based on how clearly your business entity is defined across the web, the quality and recency of content mentioning your brand, and the strength of third-party authority signals like reviews, directories, and industry publications. It synthesises all of these signals to determine which brands are most credible for a given query.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d3">
          <summary>Can I pay to be recommended by ChatGPT?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>There is no paid advertising programme within ChatGPT's recommendation engine. You cannot buy placements the way you can with Google Ads. The only way to get recommended is to strengthen the organic signals ChatGPT uses — entity data, structured markup, authoritative content, and consistent third-party mentions.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d1">
          <summary>How long does it take to get recommended by ChatGPT?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>Most businesses begin seeing improvements in ChatGPT citation rates within 30 to 90 days of implementing a GEO strategy. Quick wins like schema markup and entity optimisation can show results within weeks, while authority building compounds over several months.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d2">
          <summary>Do you guarantee ChatGPT recommendations?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>No ethical agency can guarantee a specific ChatGPT recommendation because the model updates its training data and behaviour regularly. What we guarantee is a systematic, data-driven approach that maximises your likelihood of being cited. We track citation rates across prompts monthly so you can see measurable progress.</p></div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== RELATED SERVICES ========== -->
  <section class="section" id="related-services" aria-label="Related services">
    <div class="container">
